{"tid":1549362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十點鳩叫聽日美領見，唔入香港站德福去連儂牆貼908資訊","createTime":"2019-09-07T09:46:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T01:59:25.000Z","uid":266294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c4b79c672f7b8e513ef358c3a9c83850aa7e9ed8","tid":1549362,"uid":266294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:46:19.000Z","msg":"既然有巴打表示好多人未知聽日去美領，咁不如十點順便宣傳埋啦？<br />\n可以叫埋「有不反對通知書」，增加和理非去嘅意欲<br />\n<br />\n至於想留力聽日、或者因為各種原因唔過香港站德福嘅各位，<br />\n既然你地冇乜嘢做，不如趁放工時間落街幫手等多啲人知道聽日美領請願？<br />\n除咗連儂牆貼908資訊，仲可以快閃各大屋苑大叫，將資訊傳開架，<br />\n但因為聚得太耐驚引狗，建議Hit and run或附近街坊各自做<br />\n<br />\n大家分工合作，兄弟爬山，各自努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d78c0e8b3dde0558a00df7ecffce01ccaaab6873","tid":1549362,"uid":266294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:48:16.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d0b39bf3c1a663c73380157753a23db5c5217aa","tid":1549362,"uid":41159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T01:57:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8139b3f082525b8ad962f7cd4c7ea79b39021026","tid":1549362,"uid":74929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T01:59:25.000Z","msg":"908 美領 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}